		<div id="comment_body_64715898"><p>DS1515+. 3 drives in RAID5 (if storage grows too much, will switch to a 3 way mirror).</p><p>2 64GB SSDs as cache.</p><p>2 external 2.5" drives as hyperbackup.</p><p>2 1GB eth cables directly from NAS to desktop in a bonded pair.</p><p>iSCSI drives for the steam folder and other such stuff, SMB shares for docs and stuff.</p><p>will go out of SW support around oct next year, will re-evalualate then and there</p></div>
	</div>

